title: PML-N’s Khawaja Salman wins PP-153 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Khawaja Salman Rafique of Pakistan Muslim League-Nawaz (PML-N) has won the election for Punjab Assembly constituency PP-153 Lahore-IX by securing 35,232 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was independent candidate Mian Awais Anjum, who bagged 33,027 votes.
Voters’ turn-out remained 41.4 %.
